snippet.title: Diana and Roma Pretend Play with Fun Inflatable Toys
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma play with inflatable toys. But the children are greedy and do not share them. Dad bought for children a new large inflatable toy - a rainbow with a water slide. Now Diana and Roma are playing fun together.
